MGIC Investment Corp., the mortgage
insurer that breached regulatorsâ€™ capital limits, said Chief
Investment Officer and Treasurer James Karpowicz will retire on
March 1.  Lisa Pendergast will be promoted to treasurer when
Karpowicz leaves, the Milwaukee-based company said today in a
statement distributed by PR Newswire. Karpowicz joined the
insurer in 1986 as an assistant treasurer and has held his
